# ─── Supabase — Dashboard (React / Vite) ─────────────────────────────────────
# Copy this file to apps/dashboard/.env and fill in your values.
# These are PUBLIC keys — safe to include in the browser bundle.
#
# Get these from: Supabase Dashboard → Project Settings → API

VITE_SUPABASE_URL="https://[YOUR-PROJECT-REF].supabase.co"
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY="eyJ..."

# ─── API Proxy (Vite dev server) ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# The Vite dev server proxies /api → http://localhost:3000.
# This is already configured in vite.config.ts — no changes needed here.

